---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact | Collin County Journal"
  description="Contact Collin County Journal for tips, corrections, documents, interview requests, general inquiries, and affiliated Princeton Journal matters."
  url="https://collincountyjournal.com/contact/"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-10">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">
      Contact
    </p>

    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      Contact Collin County Journal
    </h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-800">
      <p>
        For questions, corrections, tips, documents, interview requests, or general inquiries, use the form below or email us directly at <strong>collincountyjournal@gmail.com</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        We review submissions with care, but submission of a message, tip, or document does not guarantee publication, response, or follow-up.
      </p>

      <p>
        For Princeton-specific matters, registry concerns, or issues tied to pages published under The Princeton Journal, you may also contact <strong>theprincetonjournal@gmail.com</strong>.
      </p>

      <form
        name="contact"
        method="POST"
        action="/thank-you/"
        data-netlify="true"
        netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
        class="mt-8 space-y-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 p-6 shadow-sm"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />

        <p class="hidden">
          <label>
            Don’t fill this out if you’re human:
            <input name="bot-field" />
          </label>
        </p>

        <div>
          <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
            Your Email
          </label>
          <input
            type="email"
            name="email"
            required
            placeholder="you@example.com"
            class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-base outline-none focus:border-black"
          />
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
            Subject
          </label>
          <select
            name="subject"
            required
            class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-300 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base outline-none focus:border-black"
          >
            <option value="">Select a subject</option>
            <option value="News Tip">News Tip</option>
            <option value="Correction Request">Correction Request</option>
            <option value="Clarification Request">Clarification Request</option>
            <option value="Document Submission">Document Submission</option>
            <option value="Princeton Journal / Registry Concern">Princeton Journal / Registry Concern</option>
            <option value="Story Idea">Story Idea</option>
            <option value="Interview / Comment Request">Interview / Comment Request</option>
            <option value="Advertising / Sponsorship">Advertising / Sponsorship</option>
            <option value="Partnership / Collaboration">Partnership / Collaboration</option>
            <option value="Technical Issue">Technical Issue</option>
            <option value="General Inquiry">General Inquiry</option>
            <option value="Other">Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="mb-2 block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
            Message
          </label>
          <textarea
            name="message"
            rows="8"
            required
            placeholder="Write your message here..."
            class="w-full rounded-xl border border-gray-300 px-4 py-3 text-base outline-none focus:border-black"
          ></textarea>
        </div>

        <button
          type="submit"
          class="rounded-xl border border-black px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition hover:bg-black hover:text-white"
        >
          Submit
        </button>
      </form>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Tips and Documents
      </h2>

      <p>
        If you have records, documents, or information that may be relevant to the public, you may send them to the email above.
      </p>

      <p>
        If your issue involves how a public registry record appears on a Princeton Journal page, include the SID, listed name, and a short description of the issue so it can be reviewed more efficiently.
      </p>

      <p>
        We review submitted materials using editorial judgment and verification standards. Submission alone does not guarantee publication.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        Corrections and Clarifications
      </h2>

      <p>
        If you believe an article contains a factual error or needs clarification, contact us with the article, the issue you identified, and any supporting information you want us to review.
      </p>

      <p>
        When a material correction or clarification is made, it may be noted in the relevant article so readers can understand what changed.
      </p>

      <p>
        If a concern involves Princeton Journal registry presentation, displayed photos, or related public-record display issues, we can review how the material appears on the site even when the underlying official record is maintained by a government source.
      </p>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <p class="text-base text-gray-600">
        Clear communication from readers helps strengthen accountable local reporting across Collin County.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
